

<section class="top-section">
    <div class="container-fluid">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-4">
				<div class="hero-images">
					<img src="http://res.cloudinary.com/dx3z90dgl/image/upload/v1483451983/RTO12Logo_Angled-01_a4euwt.svg" alt="Rto12logo angled 01 a4euwt">
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-5">
				<div class="homepadborder">
					<h1 class="herowhiteh1">SHARE YOUR CANADA WITH THE WORLD</h1>
					<h4 class="herowhiteh4">Greetings fellow Canucks!</h4>
					<h4 class="herowhiteh4">In case you didn’t get the memo with the latest care package of maple syrup and ketchup chips, July 1st will mark the 150th anniversary of Canada.</h4>
					<h4 class="herowhiteh4">Explorers’ Edge wants to bring one lucky Canadian ex-pat back home to celebrate Canada’s 150th with us in the wilderness north of Toronto and heck – because we’re all so nice – how about a few friends from your new country tag along too?</h4>
					<h4 class="herowhiteh4">Share your passion for Canada with the world and you could be headed home for an incredible week of very Canadian adventures – on us!</h4>
